txt.en: As Celeborn leads a company of brave adventurers into the depths of the Remmorchant seeking to bring about the final defeat of his ancient foe Ungwetári, Rûkhor the Pale Herald enacts his vile plan to unleash the unending hunger of Shelob the Great upon all of Middle-earth.
Remmorchant, the Net of Darkness -- Tier 4

As Celeborn leads a company of brave adventurers into the depths of the Remmorchant seeking to bring about the final defeat of his ancient foe Ungwetári, Rûkhor the Pale Herald enacts his vile plan to unleash the unending hunger of Shelob the Great upon all of Middle-earth.
Defeat Bratha Tasakh, Thossulun, Rûkhor, and Shelob the Great on Tier 4
You have stood against the darkness and overcome the evils lurking within the Remmorchant.
